---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Robotic Palletizers — Formic Automate NOW"
  description="Fully supported robotic palletizers for food, beverage, and CPG manufacturers — end-of-line case stacking and palletizing by the month or year, one flat rate, 24/7 maintenance included."
  ogTitle="Robotic Palletizers — Formic"
  ogDescription="Fully supported robotic palletizers. No CapEx. No risk. Month-to-month, 24/7 maintenance included."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/solutions/palletizing" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/solutions">Solutions</a><span class="sep">/</span>Palletizing
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Palletizing</div>
    <h1>Robotic Palletizers.<br><em>No CapEx. No Risk.</em></h1>
    <p class="lede">Fully supported robotic palletizers for food, beverage, and CPG manufacturers: handling end-of-line case stacking and palletizing by the month or year, one flat rate, 24/7 maintenance included.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/Haviland_Products_-_Palletizing_poster.jpg">
        <source src="/Formic-Header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-cap">Automate NOW Palletizers · production cycle</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — Automate NOW</div>
      <h2>The fastest way to <em>put a robot on your line</em>.</h2>
      <p>Six palletizer options, one flat monthly rate, swap equipment mid-contract as your needs change.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>24/7 support and 100% maintenance — included</li>
        <li>Contracted performance and uptime guarantees</li>
        <li>Six system options — swap equipment anytime, same flat rate</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="https://land.formic.co/palletizer-scoping-checklist" class="larr">Palletizer scoping checklist →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Haviland_Products_-_Palletizing.gif" alt="Formic Automate NOW palletizer running at production speed" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Robotic palletizing · 24/7</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Cameron-Cobot-Palletizing.jpg" alt="Formic cobot palletizer on a CPG line" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Cobot palletizer · small footprint</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — Cobot Palletizers</div>
      <h2>Cobot Palletizers, <em>fits almost any space</em>.</h2>
      <p>Compact cobot palletizers for food, beverage, and CPG plants. Ideal for single-shift lines with lighter cases; solves labor strain without a major retrofit.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Small footprint — fits where floor space is tight</li>
        <li>Built for food, beverage & CPG single-shift lines</li>
        <li>Lighter cases, moderate rates — fully supported</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">03 — Industrial Palletizers</div>
      <h2>Industrial Palletizers, <em>built to run around the clock</em>.</h2>
      <p>For multi-shift, high-volume production. Our engineering team scopes the cell to your line: heavier cases, faster rates, taller stacks, built to run nonstop.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Continuous multi-shift throughput — heavier cases, taller stacks</li>
        <li>Engineered to your line, with four industrial unit options</li>
        <li>Full safety: fencing + area scanners, ANSI/RIA compliant</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Formic-F50-Palletizer.jpg" alt="Formic F50 industrial palletizer running on a customer line — Formic-branded KUKA arm with operator station" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Industrial palletizer · multi-shift</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">Automate NOW</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,68px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 12px">No CapEx. No New Hires. <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">No Problems.</em></h2>
    <p style="font-size:16px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(240,245,241,.6);max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 52px">Three reasons mid-market manufacturers choose Automate NOW Palletizers to beat labor, ergonomic, and productivity challenges.</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);text-align:left">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:34px 28px">
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:rgba(255,145,0,.6);margin-bottom:14px">01</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:24px;font-weight:600;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:4px">No CapEx</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange);margin-bottom:18px">Financially accessible</div>
        <ul class="feats" style="margin:0"><li>No CapEx — stretch your capital budget</li><li>Get more projects done and grow your business faster</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:34px 28px">
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:rgba(255,145,0,.6);margin-bottom:14px">02</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:24px;font-weight:600;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:4px">No New Hires</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange);margin-bottom:18px">Fully supported</div>
        <ul class="feats" style="margin:0"><li>Formic handles everything — just drop air and power</li><li>Free your maintenance team for higher-value work</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:34px 28px">
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:rgba(255,145,0,.6);margin-bottom:14px">03</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:24px;font-weight:600;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:4px">No Problems</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange);margin-bottom:18px">Totally flexible</div>
        <ul class="feats" style="margin:0"><li>Month-to-month or multi-year — start small, grow fast</li><li>Flex equipment swaps mid-contract as your needs change</li></ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/Focus-7603.jpg">
        <source src="/ATLAS_EOAT.webm" type="video/webm" />
      </video>
      <span class="img-cap">Vision-guided EOAT</span>
    </div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">Full Service Automation</div>
      <h2>Backed by <em>Full Service Automation</em>.</h2>
      <p>Every Formic palletizer runs under Full Service Automation: hardware, a dedicated engineering and maintenance team, and Formic Production Intelligence analytics built in.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Hardware, engineering, and maintenance — all included</li>
        <li>Formic Production Intelligence — real-time line data</li>
        <li>Performance and uptime you can plan around</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/full-service" class="larr">How Full Service works →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:96px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="db-tag">Proven on real floors</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,56px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.05;color:var(--black);margin:8px 0 32px">Already running, <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">every day</em>.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey)">
      <a href="/stories/land-o-frost" style="background:var(--white);padding:36px 34px;text-decoration:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px">
        <div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1;letter-spacing:-.02em">20%</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey)">Lower OpEx · Land O'Frost</div>
        <p style="font-size:15px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.6;color:var(--dgrey);margin:6px 0 0">Faster changeovers, upskilled employees, and 20% OpEx savings every day with Automate NOW Palletizers.</p>
        <span style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange);margin-top:4px">Read the story →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/stories/kari-out" style="background:var(--white);padding:36px 34px;text-decoration:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px">
        <div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1;letter-spacing:-.02em">25%</div>
        <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey)">More output · Kari-Out</div>
        <p style="font-size:15px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.6;color:var(--dgrey);margin:6px 0 0">Eliminated temp labor dependency, hit 100% uptime, and grew output by 25% with zero capital outlay and zero shipping errors.</p>
        <span style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange);margin-top:4px">Read the story →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>End the staffing crisis<br><em>at the end of your line.</em></h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="/contact/get-a-quote" class="btn-ctadark">Get a Quote</a>
    <a href="/solutions" class="btn-ctawh">All Solutions</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
